snippet.title: Ben's Worx
snippet.description:
Hello and welcome to Ben's Worx , ever since I was young I've always had an interest in woodworking, Now that I'm older I make all kinds of things, from wood, metal, plastics and my current favourite epoxy resin projects, i'll do my best to entertain you every week.

You can check out my Dragon Eggs here - https://www.etsy.com/shop/bensworx

Anyone choosing to re-enact or recreate any of my videos accepts all personal liability and or responsibility by doing so. All the tools you see in my videos are dangerous and can cause serious injury, please take proper safety training and precautions.

Want to send me something? send it to:

BENSWORX
PO BOX 3318
LOGANHOLME 4129
QLD Australia

You can stay up to date with latest projects and unseen footage @

https://www.facebook.com/bensworx1

https://twitter.com/Isbenny69

https://www.instagram.com/bens_worx/
